            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>anibus</ex></expan> Aurelio Marco duplario <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> III <expan><abbr>Ital</abbr><ex>icae</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>coniugi carissimo qui vixit <expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>os</ex></expan> XXXX et <lb n="3"/>Aurelis Marciano qui vixit <expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>os</ex></expan> XIII et <lb n="4"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>mo qui vixit <expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>os</ex></expan> XI et Maturo qui <lb n="5"/>vixit annum I <expan><abbr>mens</abbr><ex>es</ex></expan> VII filis dulcissimis <lb n="6"/>et Aureliae Severae matri bene valenti <lb n="7"/>Aurelia Decorata et sibi viva <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>aciendum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>uravit</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Die Oberfläche des Inschriftfeldes ist stellenweise stark beschädigt und schwer lesbar. Z. 4 zu Beginn noch die oberen Ansätze zweier Buchstaben zu erkennen. Späte Schrift.</p>
            </div>
